<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٥٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٠٧٢٩ -<span class="c5"> سَمِعْتُ ابْنَ جُرَيْجٍ يَقُولُ:</span> <span class="c2">«يُعْلَمُ ذَلِكَ إِذَا جَامَعَهَا فَلْيُبْرِزْهُ لَهُمْ فِي ثَوْبٍ»</span>.<span class="c5"> قَالَ عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ:</span> <span class="c2">«يَعْنِي الْمَنِيَّ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>